page.title: 12Games Children Play.
page.content: At Woodham Walter Primary School,Kim is a 2'nd year Girl.She likes to play tennis at school during her break time.During her games lesson she plays rounders and hockey.Also at break time she plays on the bars.At home she rides her bike and plays in the stream.She does running as a hobby. Her favourate thing she likes doing is riding her bike.On Mondays she goes swimming at witham with the school.Elizabeth is a 4'th year girl,She plays Rounders,Hockey and Netball in Games.In Netball she plays against other schools. At break she plays tennis and goes swimming with the school on Mondays.At home she plays with her Hamsters.Her favourate thing she likes to do is swim.She reads Adventure Books.She has'nt really got a favourate author,but her favourate book is Watership Down.
